pageProduct.name: Protein World Slender Pancakes Pouch 500g
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Low sugar, high protein pancakes - only 85 calories per pancake

Common Uses

These incredible pancakes were created so you can enjoy your food whilst transforming your body. Packed with only the highest quality ingredients & no added sugar. Designed to be effective as a meal replacement shake, but also as a perfect meal at any time, The Slender Pancakes are high in protein to support the maintenance of muscle mass and support weight loss

Ingredients

Pancake Mix [wheat flour, glucose syrup, whole egg powder, raising agents (disodium diphosphate, sodium carbonates), salt, thickener (Guar gum)], Whey Protein Concentrate (milk), natural flavourings, Protein World Vitamin & Mineral Blend (magnesium oxide, potassium chloride, ascorbic acid, mixed natural tocopherols, zinc gluconate, ferrous fumarate, vitamin K2-menaquinone, molybdenum chelate, manganese gluconate, beta carotene, cupric gluconate, nicotinamide, calcium d-pantothenate, pyridoxine hydro-chloride, thiamin hydrochloride, riboflavin, cholecalciferol, methylcobalamin, chromium picolinate, folic acid, potassium iodide, sodium selenite, d-biotin), Protein World Thermogenic Blend (Guarana Extract (22% caffeine) & Green Tea Extract (40% polyphenols), Sunflower Lecithin (emulsifier), Sucralose (sweetener)

Directions

Add 4 Scoops (50G) To 120Ml Of Milk Or Water and shake. Add 1 Tbsp of Coconut Oil to a pan and pour the pancake mixture into the centre. (The mixture should be runnier).
